{"tid":2295804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不敢相信這些姐姐們明年就40歲：人美氣質佳，她們都是「童顏美貌」的最佳示範！","createTime":"2020-11-22T04:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T11:55:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff3cb9fb7b339ec347b764e830bf89ab5a010aa","tid":2295804,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"2個月之後2021年就到來了，1982年出生的這些女明星們明年就是不惑之年「40歲」（韓國年齡）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都說歲月流逝，一定會在人們身上留下印記，但這種變化似乎並不適用於螢光幕中的女星們。因為無論過去還是現在，她們都展現了「童顏美貌」，與最近活動的20代演員相比也絲毫不遜色於她們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓志旼<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3e2a501eef013cabd7f9a97b019569d5/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-20/131780-885659.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3e2a501eef013cabd7f9a97b019569d5%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-20%2F131780-885659.png&h=4a36152e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五官精緻小巧的韓志旼也即將迎來40歲，這頭濃密烏黑還蓬鬆的頭髮是多少「禿頭」少女們羨慕的對象啊。<br />\n<br />\n孫藝珍<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b628c72522261c4b4998dc488d7fb053/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-20/131780-885660.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b628c72522261c4b4998dc488d7fb053%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-20%2F131780-885660.jpeg&h=4a4ffbb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n笑起來有著一雙極致美麗的「月牙眼」的孫藝真，很難想像姐姐明年就要40歲了，美了20年的她不管歲月如何流逝，依然能夠迷倒一眾迷弟迷妹們。<br />\n<br />\n劉寅娜<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8ecfb499f1d09981ba3aae02dbd0739d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-20/131780-885661.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8ecfb499f1d09981ba3aae02dbd0739d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-20%2F131780-885661.jpg&h=363d0100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n40歲了還依舊保持天真元氣少女感的人真的不多，劉寅娜絕對算一個，誰能受得了歐尼的撒嬌？<br />\n<br />\n金亞中<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4f99995cf8dd56c07b2fa399fe34d3db/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-20/131780-885662.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4f99995cf8dd56c07b2fa399fe34d3db%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-20%2F131780-885662.jpeg&h=98350013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n迷人的微笑，高挑的身材，緊致的S型曲線，還擁有完美時尚消化力的金亞中，真的是如同吃了防腐劑一樣，十年如一日的美麗動人。"},{"pid":"815586c5c9484d23cda2eb22c91ae036c36c13e1","tid":2295804,"uid":42402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"孫藝珍真係好正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed213abca2f2ab38acb193998cee50a75aa3fa2","tid":2295804,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815586c5c9484d23cda2eb22c91ae036c36c13e1","tid":2295804,"uid":42402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"孫藝珍真係好正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"孫藝珍黑絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27c9d5e3dfb1bfb378a0f3061a9b11544ea6370","tid":2295804,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"815586c5c9484d23cda2eb22c91ae036c36c13e1","tid":2295804,"uid":42402,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"孫藝珍真係好正式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"愛的迫肛正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f476ed5ea7ddf973c9a8c2c77843d906168d203","tid":2295804,"uid":244315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:03:05.000Z","msg":"林志玲去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa17eba9799dbae004282cc789708312c0c56c7b","tid":2295804,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"很正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da9273619fb88477eeb2f2105